      <p>When the documented steps don&rsquo;t hold, the cause is usually past the surface &mdash; a digital-signature certificate that won&rsquo;t install or stay trusted, SSL/TLS settings a Windows update changed, a security program that re-blocks the download after each reboot, or a damaged QuickBooks installation. A Certified ProAdvisor with active Desktop and Enterprise certifications diagnoses the actual root cause, fixes it against a written scope, and verifies the update completes cleanly before closing. Independent firm &mdash; not Intuit, and not Intuit&rsquo;s software support.</p>
